  "text": "After a long time hiding in my cave, I finally came out, and I have to say, EuroPython  with Junior Guru was absolutely worth it.\n\nIn the past, I was a regular at big business expos like Anuga  or SIAL Paris formal, sales-driven environments where people in suits brag about how many truckloads they sold.\n\nThis was a refreshing change. A welcoming, informal community where you feel like you’re among your own. No pretending, no posturing, just genuine people sharing knowledge, ideas, and good vibes.\n\nSo don’t be like me. Let’s crawl out of our caves and support events like these.\nEven just for the food and beer after, it’s 100% worth it.",
