      "link": "https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:ugcPost:7352667975826432000?commentUrn=urn%3Ali%3Acomment%3A%28ugcPost%3A7352667975826432000%2C7353000474872094722%29&dashCommentUrn=urn%3Ali%3Afsd_comment%3A%287353000474872094722%2Curn%3Ali%3AugcPost%3A7352667975826432000%29",
      "text": "I'm happy you had a great time! Thanks for all the feedback. It was so nice to talk to you also over beer after the day was over. And your story is so interesting - I'm really curious where this all leads you 💪\n\nAnd yes, one of the issues why people don't come to IT meetups or conferences is because they imagine something super serious and pretentious, people in suits or something. While instead, it's all very informal and friendly. I'm happy we managed to go one step further and created a safe space where anyone felt welcome to share what they had to say. That's something I really consider the biggest success of the day 🙌 Thanks for being part of this!",
